<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>People Die if They Are Killed</title>
<script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
<script type='text/javascript' src='home.js'></script>

<!-- that's right, we're using bootstrap--> 
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-rwoIResjU2yc3z8GV/NPeZWAv56rSmLldC3R/AZzGRnGxQQKnKkoFVhFQhNUwEyJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tether/1.4.0/js/tether.min.js" integrity="sha384-DztdAPBWPRXSA/3eYEEUWrWCy7G5KFbe8fFjk5JAIxUYHKkDx6Qin1DkWx51bBrb" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-vBWWzlZJ8ea9aCX4pEW3rVHjgjt7zpkNpZk+02D9phzyeVkE+jo0ieGizqPLForn" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</head>
<body>
<center>
<div class ='container'>
<h1>Bode :3's Random Encounter Generator</h1>
New from dev team Bode :3! This generator will take the inputs given and generate a random encounter.<br/>
Generator complies with D&D 5e rules for encounters, and pulls from the 5e Monster Manual.<br/>
If you're not satisfied with the encounter, feel free to reroll it.<br/><hr>
Enter a number of party members: <input type="number" id='party-number' min=1 max=20>
Enter a level: <input type="number" id='party-level' min=1 max=20>
<form>
    <fieldset>
        <legend>Environment</legend>
        <p>
            <label></label>
            <select id='environments'>
                  <% @environs.each() do |environ| %>
             <option value= "<%= environ.id()%>"> <%= environ.name() %> </option>
                <% end %>
            </select>
        </p>
    </fieldset>
</form>
Difficulty of encounter: <select id = "diff">
<option value = 1>Easy</option>
<option value = 2>Moderate</option>
<option value = 3>Difficult</option>
<option value = 4>Impossible</option>
</select><br/><br/>

<button id='generate'>Generate Encounter</button></div>
<div id = 'encounter' class='container'>
</div>
</center>
</body>
</html>
